 text and drawings and the story of his life=E2=80=94which was never easily=
 defined, would disappear completely.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom=
:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">In early 2020, Be=
