line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">With fewer <em>catalogues raisonn=C3=A9</em> be=
ing published these days,
and the need for more responsive databases, artists=E2=80=99 studios and es=
tates have turned to providing archive numbers as evidence of authenticatio=
n=E2=80=94a fairly responsive resource that helps define an object and situ=
ate it within the body of the artist=E2=80=99s work. Some estates or studio=
s=E2=80=94such as those of <strong>Philip Guston</strong>, <strong>Roy Lich=
tenstein</strong>, and <strong>Gerhard Richter</strong>=E2=80=94have compre=
hensive databases that are available to the public. Others, like the Calder=
 Foundation,
have closed systems. Good record-keeping and a responsive studio or estate =
are often necessary, though not necessarily sufficient, conditions to grow =
an artist=E2=80=99s market.=C2=A0=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bott=
om:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">And Beard=E2=80=
=99s market <em>needs</em> some growth. Although a large photo collage, <em=
>Lion at Night</em>, from 1984, sold for $327,000 in May of 2023, it=E2=80=
=99s been quite some time since top prices advanced for his work. From 2011=
 to
2017, seven different works sold at auction for prices above $300,000, incl=
uding three that achieved prices above $600,000. Since then, and especially=
 after his harrowing death, the auction market for his work has cooled.=C2=
=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;"><br/>One of the shibboleths of the art market=
 is that it is lawless and unregulated. But that=E2=80=99s not true. Auctio=
n houses and art dealers are subject to commercial laws, and more important=
ly, the market has developed its own systems of
self-regulation. The strength and quality of an artist=E2=80=99s studio or =
foundation can be the difference between their legacy dissipating into the =
ether or gathering strength with time. A spokesperson for Heritage Auctions=
 said, =E2=80=9CHeritage will be filing a response to this frivolous lawsui=
t within the next two weeks.=E2=80=9D</p></div>
